// Newline in Expression
// ERROR: Newline terminates expression before operator
x = 1
    + 2      // Parsed as: x = 1; +2; (second statement is invalid)

// This should be written as:
// x = 1 +
//     2    // Valid: line ends with operator

// Or:
// x = (1
//     + 2)  // Valid: expression in parentheses
